OL,3,CMayoral election delay is 'a move
OL,4,Ctowards totalitarianism', Tory claims
OL,6,FCandidates for mayoral elections in
OL,7,Fthe South have criticised the
OL,8,Fgovernment's move to delay them until
OL,9,F2028, after ministers said these areas
OL,10,Fneeded more time to prepare.
OL,12,FElections in nine council areas,
OL,13,Fincluding six in the Meridian region:
OL,14,FEast Sussex, West Sussex, Essex,
OL,15,FHampshire, the Isle of Wight and
OL,16,FSurrey, were already postponed to next
OL,17,Fyear amid the reorganisation of local
OL,18,Fgovernment in England.
